---
title: Indian Chicken, Potato & Cauliflower Korma Soup with Tortilla Wedges, Cashew Nuts & Coriander
description: Be sure your spoon is at the ready because this korma soup is going to disappear in seconds. It has everything, roasted cauliflower and potato, chicken and aromatic mild curry flavours. Dip the tortilla wedges in for a bit of fun.

